    "# 2. Data Preprocessing:\n",
    "- Handle missing values (e.g., imputation).\n",
    "- Encode categorical variables."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "id": "e31fdaeb-445e-4492-95c3-8115ef49bbc0",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
